data.name: checkBoxX2.SuperTooltip
data.value:
This application converts the text you type into the textboxes automatically to hexadecimal. If you dont want that to happen, you can check this checkbox and then you have to type in the hexadecimal into the textboxes yourself.
You don't want to do this unless you know what you're doing :)
